          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Walnut is one of the best schools in Pune. They have the innovative way of teaching where students learn the concept quite easily.The plus point being the bagless school. Parents are aware with what child learns everyday through the Walsh app. Also the worksheets are send on weekly basis. Hence it is hassle free journey for both students and parents. The yearly timetable is shared. The electric Saturday's which involves various cocurricular activities for child along with parents happen in the given timeslot. The school also gives preference to sports in daily schedule. All the Hindu festivals are celebrated at school. The unique idea of celebrating child's birthday with \"Aukshan\" ceremony was overwhelming and suprising. The yearly walnut carnival was very well organised.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
